Hey there!

Solidsnake and Hamster are back again with an dev-map :)

Aim future_arena is created by hamster, and solidsnake did the finishing touch + lightning. 
Origionally we wanted to release it friday, but because of a few bugs we decided to do it now :)

So, after a bunch of compiles, it is here, and we are both happy with it :)

this map contains:
32 spawnpoints
buyzones
env_cubemaps xD

Soon wel be releasing a updated version of this map with some specials effects and a couple of bugs fixed!

-have fun
--Hamster and SolidSnake out
